post_summaries.description: The Instagram post by tatupatiala is a video. The visible frame shows a text overlay on a shimmering gold background that reads "People with great passion can." The post has 99 likes and was posted on February 1, 2023.

The Instagram post is an advertisement for the Wisdom app, inviting users to ask the poster questions and receive voice replies. The profile name is "tatupatiala" and the bio mentions "PATCHA • Passion". Another post in the feed has some text in a language other than English.

The image is an Instagram post by tatupatiala. It features a political advertisement for Jarmo Limnéll, a candidate for Kansanedustaja (likely a member of parliament) from the KOKOOMUS party. The post includes text in Finnish praising Limnéll's qualities and encouraging people to vote for him. The caption thanks someone for the recommendation and includes the hashtag #kirkkonummenkokoomus.

The image is an Instagram post featuring two men, presumably politicians, promoting a candidate for local elections. The post is in Finnish and includes the hashtag #kirkkonummenkokoomus, suggesting a connection to the National Coalition Party in Kirkkonummi, Finland. The number "198" is prominently displayed, likely representing the candidate's number on the ballot.

The image is a motivational graphic with the text "You are great," "If you can't be a bridge... be a lighthouse," and "You are amazing!" It also shows a simple drawing of a bridge and a lighthouse. The post is captioned "I am Youniverse" with some emojis. The audio to the post is Coldplay's "The Scientist".

The image is a screen capture of an Instagram post. The post is a short video clip with the text "POV: He is the best professor ever." The clip appears to be from a classroom setting, featuring a professor and students. The caption of the post is "How to understand others?"
